<p begin="00:15:24.860" end="00:15:25.860" style="s2">guide the scientific method.]</p>
<p begin="00:15:25.860" end="00:15:32.209" style="s2">And by the time we get to Kant, the Empiricist<br />tradition is largely unable to respond to</p>
