<p begin="00:16:14.600" end="00:16:20.360" style="s2">is filtered and structured by these pre-existing<br />cognitive structures as well.”</p>
<p begin="00:16:20.360" end="00:16:26.059" style="s2">Now the problem with that side of the line—and<br />this is also well worked out by the time you</p>
