<p begin="00:17:07.680" end="00:17:12.320" style="s2">So once again, you’re stuck in a rather<br />subjective place.</p>
<p begin="00:17:12.320" end="00:17:16.480" style="s2">And again, the importance of Kant here is<br />then he’s also looking at this more Rationalist</p>
