<p begin="00:31:20.480" end="00:31:25.890" style="s2">the big question we have to turn to is to<br />say, How do we judge whether something works?</p>
<p begin="00:31:25.890" end="00:31:26.890" style="s2">Yes.</p>
<p begin="00:31:26.890" end="00:31:35.930" style="s2">Or how do I say that, “It’s good because<br />I get what I want” or “We get what we</p>
<p begin="00:31:35.930" end="00:31:42.230" style="s2">want.” Well, what is a “want”? And where<br />did these “wants” come from? And why should</p>
