<p begin="00:31:50.960" end="00:31:55.410" style="s2">Right, okay. That’s right. So you can start<br />to question the framework, the validity of</p>
<p begin="00:31:55.410" end="00:31:58.080" style="s2">the framework within which you’re constructing<br />the answer.</p>
<p begin="00:31:58.080" end="00:32:01.740" style="s2">That’s right. And at this point we’re<br />reading epistemology [epistemology: the theory</p>
