<p begin="00:34:35.190" end="00:34:36.190" style="s2">Exactly.</p>
<p begin="00:34:36.190" end="00:34:38.520" style="s2">So you can spin off down that aisle.</p>
<p begin="00:34:38.520" end="00:34:42.220" style="s2">And that’s the other thing I really want<br />to talk to you about, because on the one hand</p>
