<p begin="00:34:59.090" end="00:35:06.040" style="s2">that has its origin more in political revolution<br />and class-based theory, and they do that under</p>
<p begin="00:35:06.040" end="00:35:11.660" style="s2">the guise of pure philosophy, in some sense,<br />but with the intent and motivation of something</p>
<p begin="00:35:11.660" end="00:35:18.080" style="s2">like justifying the social revolution, or<br />continuing the Marxist analysis of power differential.</p>
<p begin="00:35:18.080" end="00:35:22.380" style="s2">It can go both ways, yes. Right? It is possible<br />to follow the road that we’ve just been</p>
