<p begin="00:35:36.980" end="00:35:42.030" style="s2">do—so we might introduce as a corrective<br />a socializing of the process.</p>
<p begin="00:35:42.030" end="00:35:43.030" style="s2">Right.</p>
<p begin="00:35:43.030" end="00:35:46.130" style="s2">So we might then say, No, it’s not so much<br />what you want as an individual, but rather</p>
