<p begin="00:36:51.620" end="00:36:52.620" style="s2">goals or norms …</p>
<p begin="00:36:52.620" end="00:36:53.620" style="s2">Right.</p>
<p begin="00:36:53.620" end="00:37:00.030" style="s2">… and so then you’re into what the critics<br />are going to call “imperialism” of the</p>
