<p begin="00:38:31.450" end="00:38:34.880" style="s2">the idea of, say, “general narratives”<br />or “universal moral claims.”</p>
<p begin="00:38:34.880" end="00:38:38.680" style="s2">Okay, now that’s also right. That’s the<br />other way to say that. Rather than starting</p>
