<p begin="01:20:02.920" end="01:20:04.590" style="s2">Yes, that’s remarkable. That’s remarkable.</p>
<p begin="01:20:04.590" end="01:20:06.929" style="s2">Yes, so I’m very happy about that …</p>
<p begin="01:20:06.929" end="01:20:09.599" style="s2">For any book, let alone an academic book.</p>
<p begin="01:20:09.599" end="01:20:15.380" style="s2">Yes, and then multiple translations, and those<br />continue, so I’m happy about that.</p>
<p begin="01:20:15.380" end="01:20:23.929" style="s2">Now I’d say the scholarly responses have<br />been from moderate liberals: so kind of traditional</p>
