<p begin="01:20:53.829" end="01:20:56.999" style="s2">Well, it might be a sign of respect.</p>
<p begin="01:20:56.999" end="01:21:00.821" style="s2">Well there is one sign of respect that comes<br />out, and that is that every… I’d say once</p>
