<p begin="01:21:40.079" end="01:21:44.210" style="s2">So I think they are aware of me, but there<br />hasn’t really been any direct intellectual</p>
<p begin="01:21:44.210" end="01:21:46.760" style="s2">engagement, which is kind of sad.</p>
<p begin="01:21:46.760" end="01:21:53.769" style="s2">Right. Yes. So now when you set yourself up<br />to write the book, were you thinking of writing</p>
