<p begin="01:22:00.110" end="01:22:06.869" style="s2">Well, right now I’m working on the critique.<br />The first book ends—I don’t want to say</p>
<p begin="01:22:06.869" end="01:22:14.760" style="s2">abruptly—but it does end with the door open<br />to saying: How then do we respond to this</p>
<p begin="01:22:14.760" end="01:22:20.920" style="s2">dead end of Counter-Enlightenment thought<br />in postmodernism? So we’re at a point culturally</p>
