<p begin="01:26:33.130" end="01:26:37.030" style="s2">Well said. I agree one-hundred percent. Nicely<br />put.</p>
<p begin="01:26:37.030" end="01:26:39.349" style="s2">All right. Well, it was a pleasure speaking<br />with you—it was very much worthwhile.</p>
